description.p:
In an embodiment the paste comprises
25 to 35 wt. % allulose;
20 to 30 wt. % dairy butter;
10 to 14 wt. % MCT oil;
8 to 15 wt. % inulin;
4 to 8 wt. % buttermilk powder;
0.8 to 2 wt. % gum acacia;
made up to 100 wt. % with water.

The paste may be suitable for people following a vegan ketogenic diet. In an embodiment the paste comprises
25 to 35 wt. % allulose;
20 to 30 wt. % almond butter;
10 to 14 wt. % MCT oil;
8 to 15 wt. % inulin;
0.8 to 2 wt. % gum acacia;
0.5 to 1 wt. % turmeric:

In an embodiment the paste comprises
40 to 45 wt. % allulose;
8 to 15 wt. % high yield soluble coffee powder
20 to 25 wt. % dairy butter;
10 to 14 wt. % MCT oil;
made up to 100 wt. % with water.

The paste may comprise ingredients associated with indulgence and beauty. In an embodiment the paste comprises
35 to 40 wt. % sucrose;
8 to 15 wt. % high yield soluble coffee powder;
8 to 12 wt. % white chocolate;
25 to 30 wt. % coconut cream;
4 to 8 wt. % almond butter;
4 to 6 wt. % collagen powder;
0.001 to 0.003 wt. % biotin;

The paste may comprise matcha tea. In an embodiment the paste comprises
4 to 8 wt. % matcha powder;
40 to 50 wt. % sucrose;
30 to 34 wt. % coconut cream;
8 to 12 wt. % almond butter;
2 to 5 wt. % inulin;
0.5 to 2 wt. % gum acacia;
